  "informal_statement": "The cardinality of an indexed union of finite sets (over an index set s, each index i contributing the set t i) is at most the sum of the individual cardinalities — the finite-union generalization of card_union_le.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Directly `Finset.card_biUnion_le`.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem card_biUnion_le' (s : Finset ℕ) (t : ℕ → Finset ℕ) : (s.biUnion t).card ≤ ∑ i ∈ s, (t i).card",
